cu.explanation_en: Setting SCTP_INSTREAMS to 0 will cause invalid SCTP stream configuration and prevent proper F1 interface communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting att_tx to a negative value (-1) will cause invalid transmit attenuation configuration and signal transmission issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將 att_tx 設定為負值 (-1) 會導致無效的發射衰減配置，並造成訊號傳輸問題。
